io.github.teamfractal.entity

Class LandPlot

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.teamfractal.entity.LandPlot

  • public class LandPlot
extends java.lang.Object
    Holds all data relating to a single plot including: who owns it, what kind of roboticon it has on it, how much of each resource it produces

    • Constructor Detail

      • LandPlot

        public LandPlot(int ore,
                int energy,
                int food)
        Initialise LandPlot with specific base amount of resources that it could produce.

        Note: the plot will not produce this amount of each resource each turn it will only produce the type of resource that matches the customisation of the roboticon that is placed on it

        Parameters:
        ore - Amount of ore that this plot can produce per turn
        energy - Amount of energy that this plot can produce per turn
        food - Amount of food that this plot can produce per turn
